    "question": "等腰三角形ABC中，AB = AC，∠A = 30°，BC = 6 cm，求AB。",
    "answer": "6 cm",
    "steps": [
      "在等腰三角形中，AB = AC。",
      "∠A = 30°，则∠B = ∠C = (180° - 30°) ÷ 2 = 75°。",
      "使用正弦定理：AB/sin C = BC/sin A。",
      "AB = (6 × sin 75°) ÷ sin 30° = 6 cm。"
    ],
